{"id": "art-5491", "label": "Art. 5491", "title": "Art. 5491: Procedura de confiscare sau de desfiinţare a unui înscris în cazul clasării", "slug": "art-5491", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_230589675\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1172\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_230589675\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 549<sup>1</sup>:\nProcedura de confiscare sau de desfiin&#355;are a unui înscris în cazul\nclas&#259;rii </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1074352893\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1171\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1074352893\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)În cazul în care procurorul a dispus clasarea sau\nrenun&#355;area la urm&#259;rirea penal&#259;, confirmat&#259; de\njudec&#259;torul de camer&#259; preliminar&#259;, &#351;i sesizarea\njudec&#259;torului de camer&#259; preliminar&#259; în vederea lu&#259;rii\nm&#259;surii de siguran&#355;&#259; a confisc&#259;rii speciale sau a\ndesfiin&#355;&#259;rii unui înscris, ordonan&#355;a de clasare sau, dup&#259;\ncaz, ordonan&#355;a prin care s-a dispus renun&#355;area la urm&#259;rire\npenal&#259; confirmat&#259; de judec&#259;torul de camer&#259;\npreliminar&#259;, înso&#355;it&#259; de dosarul cauzei, se înainteaz&#259;\ninstan&#355;ei c&#259;reia i-ar reveni, potrivit legii, competen&#355;a s&#259;\njudece cauza în prim&#259; instan&#355;&#259;, dup&#259; expirarea termenului\nprev&#259;zut la art. 339 alin. (4) ori, dup&#259; caz, la art. 340 sau\ndup&#259; pronun&#355;area hot&#259;rârii prin care plângerea a fost\nrespins&#259; ori prin care a fost confirmat&#259; ordonan&#355;a de\nrenun&#355;are la urm&#259;rire penal&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_411987212\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1170\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_411987212\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Judec&#259;torul de camer&#259; preliminar&#259;\nstabile&#351;te termenul de solu&#355;ionare, în func&#355;ie de complexitatea\n&#351;i particularit&#259;&#355;ile cauzei, care nu poate fi mai scurt de 30 de\nzile.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_456882940\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1169\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_456882940\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Pentru termenul fixat se dispune\nîncuno&#351;tin&#355;area procurorului &#351;i se citeaz&#259; persoanele ale\nc&#259;ror drepturi sau interese legitime pot fi afectate, c&#259;rora li se\ncomunic&#259; o copie a ordonan&#355;ei, punându-le în vedere c&#259; în termen\nde 20 de zile de la primirea comunic&#259;rii pot depune note scrise.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1953340962\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1168\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1953340962\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Judec&#259;torul de camer&#259; preliminar&#259; se\npronun&#355;&#259; prin încheiere, în &#351;edin&#355;&#259; public&#259;,\ndup&#259; ascultarea procurorului &#351;i a persoanelor ale c&#259;ror drepturi\nsau interese legitime pot fi afectate, dac&#259; sunt prezente.\nDispozi&#355;iile cuprinse în titlul III al p&#259;r&#355;ii speciale privind\njudecata care nu sunt contrare dispozi&#355;iilor prezentului articol se\naplic&#259; în mod corespunz&#259;tor.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1451394839\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1167\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1451394839\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Judec&#259;torul\nde camer&#259; preliminar&#259;, solu&#355;ionând cererea, poate dispune una\ndintre urm&#259;toarele solu&#355;ii:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1643095424\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1166\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1643095424\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)respinge propunerea &#351;i dispune, dup&#259; caz,\nrestituirea bunului ori ridicarea m&#259;surii asigur&#259;torii luate în\nvederea confisc&#259;rii;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_891642538\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1165\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_891642538\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)admite propunerea &#351;i dispune confiscarea bunurilor\nori, dup&#259; caz, desfiin&#355;area înscrisului.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2052915565\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1164\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2052915565\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6)În termen de 3 zile de la comunicarea încheierii,\nprocurorul &#351;i persoanele prev&#259;zute la alin. (3) pot face, motivat,\ncontesta&#355;ie. Contesta&#355;ia nemotivat&#259; este inadmisibil&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1578447188\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1163\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1578447188\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(7)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Contesta&#355;ia\nse solu&#355;ioneaz&#259; potrivit procedurii prev&#259;zute la alin. (4) de\nc&#259;tre judec&#259;torul de camer&#259; preliminar&#259; de la instan&#355;a\nierarhic superioar&#259; celei sesizate ori, când instan&#355;a sesizat&#259;\neste Înalta Curte de Casa&#355;ie &#351;i Justi&#355;ie, de c&#259;tre\ncompletul competent potrivit legii, care poate dispune una dintre\nurm&#259;toarele solu&#355;ii:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1194745951\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1162\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1194745951\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)respinge contesta&#355;ia ca tardiv&#259;,\ninadmisibil&#259; sau nefondat&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_8539094\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1161\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_8539094\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)admite contesta&#355;ia, desfiin&#355;eaz&#259;\nîncheierea &#351;i rejudec&#259; propunerea potrivit alin. (5).</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'><span style='color:black'>TITLUL V:Executarea hot&#259;rârilor penale</span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'><span style='color:black'>CAPITOLUL I:Dispozi&#355;ii generale</span></b></p>"}